# ===========================================
# NOTES
# ===========================================

# This .gitignore file is designed for WordPress plugin development
# It excludes common files that shouldn't be tracked in version control
# 
# Key exclusions:
# - Plugin ZIP files (distribution packages)
# - Operating system files
# - IDE/Editor specific files
# - WordPress core files (if testing locally)
# - Development tool files
# - Temporary and backup files
# - Sensitive configuration files
#
# If you need to include a file that's being ignored, use:
# git add -f filename
